220
00:13:59,505 --> 00:14:02,634
- Esta é Phoebe.
- Oi, prazer.

221
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:03,847
- Joey.
- Oi.

222
00:14:04,010 --> 00:14:05,182
- Joey.
- Meu irmão, Ross.

223
00:14:05,595 --> 00:14:06,938
- Oi.
- E Rachel.

224
00:14:07,138 --> 00:14:08,560
Oi.

225
00:14:10,808 --> 00:14:14,278
